---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="홈"
  description="앵무새 브리딩과 소프트웨어 엔지니어링의 융합의 과정을 기록하는 Naviary 테크 블로그입니다."
>
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-20 px-6">
    <section class="mb-20">
      <div
        class="flex items-center gap-2 text-primary font-mono text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-4"
      >
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">terminal</span>
        <span>Engineering for Parrots & Software</span>
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-6xl font-black tracking-tight mb-6">
        Naviary <span class="text-primary">DevLog</span>
      </h1>

      <p class="text-zinc-400 text-xl leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
        반갑습니다. <span class="text-zinc-100 font-medium">황창환</span>입니다. <br
        />
        앵무새 브리딩 아키텍처와 분산 시스템 설계를 연구하며 기록합니다.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="grid gap-8">
      <div class="p-8 border border-zinc-800 rounded-2xl bg-zinc-900/30">
        <h2
          class="text-zinc-500 text-xs uppercase tracking-tighter mb-4 font-mono"
        >
          Font Test
        </h2>

        <p class="text-2xl mb-6">
          이 문장은 <span class="font-bold text-primary">Pretendard Subset</span
          >으로 렌더링됩니다. (가독성 체크)
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-2">
          <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 font-mono italic">
            // Fira Code Ligatures Test
          </p>
          <code
            class="block bg-black p-4 rounded-lg text-sm leading-relaxed border border-zinc-800"
          >
            <span class="text-blue-400">const</span>
            <span class="text-yellow-200">naviary</span> = () <span
              class="text-purple-400">=&gt;</span
            > &#123; <br />
            &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="text-blue-400">if</span> (status <span
              class="text-purple-400">!=</span
            >
            <span class="text-green-400">'perfect'</span>) <span
              class="text-blue-400">return</span
            >
            <span class="text-red-400">false</span>; <br />
            &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="text-blue-400">return</span>
            <span class="text-red-400">true</span>; <br />
            &#125;
          </code>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
